Text: 4-3-07 3:08 EST It is currently seeded and will be seeded for the remainder of the evening
For some reason its the size of a typical keylogger, suspicious.

To run two copies of GW at once: http://www.guildwarsguru.com/forum/showthread.php?t=27103

To pre-decompress all maps (and files for that matter): Create a short-cut to gw.exe, go into properties of the shortcut and in the target box put "-image" (without the quote marks) at the end (with a space between the .exe location and "-image")

That way you don't have to download this shite.
